			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">NORMAL COURSE CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Change shot direction -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Left and Right Directional Buttons</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Change camera viewpoint (up and down) - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Up and Down Directional Buttons</font>

			<br>&nbsp; Hit the ball - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
            	<br>&nbsp; Change camera viewpoint (retreat) - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
			<br>&nbsp; Change camera viewpoint (advance) - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Change shot mode - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>

                  <br>&nbsp; Select the club - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 or L1 Buttons</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Return the view point, scatter grass - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Display entire hole - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; View score - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font><br>

			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ON THE GREEN CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Change putting direction - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Left and Right Directional Buttons</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Change camera viewpont (up and down) - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Up and Down Directional Buttons</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Putt - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>

                  <br>&nbsp; Change camera viewpoint (retreat) - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Change camera viewpoint (advance) - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Change putting mode - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; View from other side - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 Button</font>

                  <br>&nbsp; Display unevenness - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Return the view point, scatter grass - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Display entire green - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font>

			<br>&nbsp; View score - 
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font><br><br>
