                  <br>&nbsp;Mirror Characters: At the character select menu highlight a golfer - &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">hold L1 and press X</font>&nbsp;
                  <br>&nbsp;Mirrored Courses: While choosing a course - &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">hold L1 + L2</font>&nbsp;
                  <br>&nbsp;Quick Reset: At any time - &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">hold L1 + L2 + R1 + R2 + Start + Select</font>&nbsp;<br>
